{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d77c212c5c","title":"救救孩子！！“广场”在难产中！！","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"096d8e1da1","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":6,"articleId":"d77c212c5c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"c916c81c62","name":"张元勋"},{"id":"f66a6976b6","name":"沈泽宜"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9273b6c22a","type":"title","text":"救救孩子！！“广场”在难产中！！","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"3d48778cdf","type":"authors","text":"北京大学张元勋沈泽宜","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"50381b4bfc","type":"subtitle","text":"（张元勋、沈泽宜：北京大学中文系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"001df0dcee","type":"subtitle","text":"救救孩子！！“广场”在难产中！！      《广场》编委会","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"8f88cbffab","type":"paragraph","text":"同学自办刊物，在难产中期待同学们全力支持。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"94f42286de","type":"paragraph","text":"在党中央大鸣大放，开门整风政策的鼓舞下，从五月十九日起我们北大同学发扬了光荣的历史传统，勇敢的站在运动前列。由于考期临近，第一个高潮已经过去。可以断言，为此运动深刻意义所决定，规模更大的高潮还在后面。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"69c3613da3","type":"paragraph","text":"在第一次高潮中，我们出色的利用了大字报，油印小报，辩论会等形式，向“三害”作了坚决的冲击。这些形式各有其优点，但也有其局限性，同学们愈来愈强烈的感觉到：一个同学们自办的铅印刊物是必不可少的。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"69004cf8eb","type":"paragraph","text":"为了更好的帮助党整风，在许多同学们的激动下，综合性刊物“广场”编委会宣告成立。“广场”是同学们自己的刊物，它的全部工作依靠同学们来办，向每一位同学开放。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"918e9015d8","type":"paragraph","text":"同学们！“广场”是民主墙的产儿，是“五一九”运动的产儿，是同学们自己的畅所欲言的园地。但是，“广场”在难产中。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"1aebd27929","type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的同学们，“广场”向你们呼吁，我们这一群大除了一颗心和一支笔以外，没有掌握任何物质手段，校方也不给我们以任何支持。同学们！救救难产中的孩子吧。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"92b5ac5c69","type":"paragraph","text":"目前我们的主要困难是经费不足。同志们！捐献吧!贷款吧!预购吧!多至一百元，少至一分钱，“广场”都将给以最大的感激。伸出你们援助的手吧!","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"43deed60ee","type":"paragraph","text":"“广场”为铅印刊物，每期暂定价二角，多退少补。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"255879d1fa","type":"subtitle","text":"第一期为“民主墙”专辑要目如下：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"67d839b384","type":"paragraph","text":"报导发刊词　　　    人之歌","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"3f2b4197da","type":"paragraph","text":"“五一九”纪事　　　整风短歌","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"abad3e704a","type":"paragraph","text":"“是时候了”    　　杜真诗两首","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"9efe29650d","type":"paragraph","text":"独白","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"37e0afadf3","type":"paragraph","text":"戴佳珊词选","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"8c8b9f94c9","type":"paragraph","text":"新乐府(国风：东山)","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"8f9c18b673","type":"paragraph","text":"民主广场","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"e9b51763ad","type":"paragraph","text":"论当前民主运动的领导","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"122bfafdee","type":"paragraph","text":"论无阶级社会中人之等级","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"6d6f24b7c0","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反论纲    　　论人事档案制度","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"8e0e055696","type":"paragraph","text":"论党领导    　　高度集权是危险的。治标还是治本。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"724f61084a","type":"paragraph","text":"论斩草除根    　怎么办？","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"b7e90bfbc6","type":"paragraph","text":"不要那样想    　周铎的遭遇","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"e213c76ce2","type":"paragraph","text":"整风运动在北大(照片)    要更勇敢的飞翔(歌曲)","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"cd540e996d","type":"paragraph","text":"临时编委会：主编：张元勋、付主编：沈泽宜、王国乡","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"685f3cf1d2","type":"paragraph","text":"编委：王国乡、叶于生、沈泽宜、李亚白、梁次平、袁鲁林、陈奉孝、张元勋、张景中、陆志华、崔德甫、龙英华","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"},{"id":"8a2f91ec1a","type":"paragraph","text":" 1957．6．6","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c"}],"page":{"id":"a53d212134","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d77c212c5c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}